QUANTUM AI HEALTHCARE: COMPREHENSIVE TECHNICAL IMPLEMENTATION

1.0 SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE SPECIFICATIONS

1.1 Core Infrastructure Requirements

1.1.1 Quantum Computing Infrastructure

```
Hardware Requirements (Phase 1 - 2025-2030):
├─ Central Quantum Processing Centers (10 globally):
│  ├─ Location: Distributed across continents
│  ├─ Quantum Processors:
│  │  ├─ Type 1: Gate-based superconducting (IBM, Google style)
│  │  │  ├─ Qubits: 10,000+ physical qubits per system
│  │  │  ├─ Coherence time: >1ms
│  │  │  ├─ Gate fidelity: >99.9%
│  │  │  └─ Connectivity: All-to-all or heavy-hex
│  │  ├─ Type 2: Photonic quantum computers
│  │  │  ├─ Qubits: 100+ logical qubits
│  │  │  ├─ Room temperature operation
│  │  │  ├─ Native for quantum networking
│  │  │  └─ Speed: 10GHz clock rates
│  │  └─ Type 3: Neutral atom arrays
│  │     ├─ Qubits: 1000+ with high connectivity
│  │     ├─ Mid-circuit measurement
│  │     └─ Good for quantum simulation
│  ├─ Classical Computing:
│  │  ├─ HPC clusters: 1000+ nodes, 10+ PFLOPS each
│  │  ├─ GPU arrays: 1000+ A100/H100 equivalents
│  │  ├─ Storage: 100+ PB each, 1ms access
│  │  └─ Networking: 400Gbps internal, 100Gbps external
│  ├─ Cryogenics:
│  │  ├─ Dilution refrigerators: 10mK base temperature
│  │  ├─ Cooling capacity: 1W at 100mK
│  │  ├─ Redundancy: N+1 systems
│  │  └─ Automation: Self-tuning, remote monitoring
│  └─ Power & Environment:
    ├─ Power: 10MW per center, dual feeds, 99.9999% uptime
    ├─ Cooling: 5MW cooling capacity, water + air hybrid
    ├─ Vibration isolation: <1nm RMS, 1-100Hz
    └─ EMI shielding: <1μT magnetic field, <1V/m electric field

├─ Edge Quantum Nodes (1000+ hospitals):
│  ├─ Quantum Processors: 100-1000 qubit systems
│  ├─ Purpose: Real-time inference, local data processing
│  ├─ Connectivity: Direct Quantum 6G satellite links
│  ├─ Uptime: 99.9%
│  └─ Maintenance: Remote diagnostics, hot-swappable modules

└─ Quantum Cloud Platform:
  ├─ API: RESTful quantum computing services
  ├─ Orchestration: Kubernetes for quantum workloads
  ├─ Scheduling: Quantum job queue with priority
  ├─ Security: QKD for all communications
  └─ Billing: Quantum compute credits (QCC) system
```

