│  ├─ Jitter: <0.1ms
│  └─ Reliability: 99.9999% (5 minutes downtime per year)
├─ Redundancy:
│  ├─ Dual satellite links
│  ├─ Terrestrial fiber backup
│  ├─ Automatic failover
│  └─ Quality of service: Highest priority
├─ Security:
│  ├─ Quantum key distribution (new key every second)
│  ├─ Quantum digital signatures on all commands
│  ├─ Intrusion detection with quantum AI
│  └─ Emergency local autonomy if connection lost
└─ Monitoring:
├─ Real-time network health
├─ Predictive maintenance
├─ Usage logging for improvement
└─ Regulatory compliance tracking

